nodes.text: Nensu Kaatik was a male Chagrian Senator of the Galactic Federation of Free Alliances who served as the Chair of the Senate. In 44 ABY, he was present when Ivaar Workan, posing as Kameron Suldar, nominated Padnel Ovin as a candidate for Chief of State following the fragmentation of the ruling Triumvirate. He was replaced by Suldar who took his place as Chair of the Senate.
